{"tid":398211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港教育大學女生企圖自殺獲救","createTime":"2017-09-13T04:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T14:12:12.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99cd89d72a5f188feabc6effefccc59ef3419939","tid":398211,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170913/large/1505275585_f349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170913%2Flarge%2F1505275585_f349.jpg&h=49de9424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因民主牆事件鬧出滿城風波的香港教育大學，早上10時許，保安報警，指有一名年約20歲的女生聲稱自殺，被職員制止。警員到場調查，女事主安全無受傷，由一名女職員陪同下送院檢查。據悉，女生就讀二年級，透露不開心。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"f2c580f2ecc6de07f8306203a4b041cbe816a088","tid":398211,"uid":54344,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"@蔡若蓮<br />\n<br />\n副局講兩句？"},{"pid":"65c37d27e2d190b54af90b706bb6bbbc9a8f1ee2","tid":398211,"uid":61207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"兩個都嫌少"},{"pid":"bcfbccaaed49dacf8aed41aa4f6d8559ce6a06fb","tid":398211,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"因學?"},{"pid":"e1548ad7467c9440c7486f2a9fe1e8380c95ed8d","tid":398211,"uid":31237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因學?</blockquote><br />\n因大"},{"pid":"47621d5b05ac3ab7fc7fd4cf2c05b451170ef9b3","tid":398211,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因學?</blockquote><br />\n因大</blockquote><br />\n白報"},{"pid":"c9a6c28eca5b1d1a3abcfa231d339dce30f20